brand new equipment in many cases right off the 
assembly line to perform those wartime missions.

02:31.259 --> 02:36.184
So it's gone from absolute depths to what I feel is 
the best of all worlds. So from the 50s to the 80s.

02:38.367 --> 02:39.889
That's pretty well the time frame. That's not to 
